step_data.thought: I clicked on the 'DESIGN' tab, but it did not lead to any section related to 'Design Schedule' or 'Theme Changes'. The current page shows configuration options for default themes and store views, but there is no specific section for theme changes or a schedule. Given the lack of relevant options, I will now check if there are any links or buttons that could potentially lead to the Design Schedule. I will hover over and click on the 'Default View' button to see if it reveals any additional sections.
